      "message": "Patch Set 6: Looks good to me, but someone else must approve\n\n(6 inline comments)\n\nSome improvements that I noticed while looking at this patch that should probably be done in a separate patch, if not already in a patch.\n\nOne concern is about discarding the return code from wait_event_interruptible().  I haven't looked at the implications of this, but that would need to be addressed in this patch if there are any, otherwise it will likely be forgotten.",
